42#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
43# include <config.h>
44#endif /* HAVE_CONFIG_H */
45#include <am_defs.h>
46#include <amu.h>
47
48
49bool_t
50xdr_amq_string(XDR *xdrs, amq_string *objp)
51{
52 if (!xdr_string(xdrs, objp, AMQ_STRLEN)) {
53 return (FALSE);
54 }
55 return (TRUE);
56}
57
58
59bool_t
60xdr_amq_sync_umnt(XDR *xdrs, amq_sync_umnt *objp)
61{
62
63 if (!xdr_opaque(xdrs, (char *) objp, sizeof(*objp))) {
64 return (FALSE);
65 }
66 return (TRUE);
67}
